":1.75},{"width":2560,"height":1438,"file_path":"/2wMxAnJrvp009k67Y5CjmL9dTGl.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1824,"height":1026,"file_path":"/r9OnfsRL2ox0ecB6m7gs5HwovnW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1824,"height":1026,"file_path":"/y6VumLjzovNnXm4DnmtbHY6CQtd.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1824,"height":1026,"file_path":"/qXkBUZ82OMLcwxPp6nWIp00QE1B.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T14:24:35.518+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"A Brighter Summer Day","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A boy experiences first love, friendships and injustices growing up in 1960s Taiwan."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"牯岭街少年杀人事件","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"这部由杨德昌执导的台湾电影杰作，被誉为当代影坛最受推崇与渴求的作品之一。影片以六十年代初的台湾为背景，改编自一起震动全岛的真实案件。这部兼具宏大格局与私密情感的巨作，以小说般的笔触与沉静的凝视，聚焦一位少年（张震的银幕首秀）从纯真逐渐无可挽回地滑向犯罪深渊的过程，并交织着躁动青春、摇滚乐与政治动荡的压抑时代底色。[标准收藏公司]"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Ein Sommer zum Verlieben","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Taipei im Jahr 1960. Der 14-jährige Schüler Chang Chen, von allen Xiao Si'r („kleine Vier“, da er das vierte von fünf Kindern ist) genannt, hatte im letzten Jahr in einem Fach eine mangelhafte Note erhalten. Obwohl alle anderen Fächer erfolgreich liefen und er eigentlich ein guter Schüler ist, musste er von der „Tagesschule“ auf die „Abendschule“ wechseln. Sein Vater, ein Regierungsbeamter aus dem Mittelstand, ist darüber unglücklich, denn die abendlich stattfindenden Schulen besitzen einen schlechten Ruf. Auf der von militärischer Strenge geprägten Schule werden die Schüler von den Lehrern oft nur mit den ihnen zugeteilten Nummern angesprochen. Die Bedenken des Vaters sind nicht grundlos: Zwischen den Little Park Boys und den 217s, zwei Jugendbanden, kommt es immer wieder zu brutalen Auseinandersetzungen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Un día de verano","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Taiwan, años '60. Los jóvenes taiwaneses, aunque dominados por China, se sienten deslumbrados por los Estados Unidos y organizan bandas para afirmar su identidad. La versión original duraba 237 minutos, pero por motivos comerciales Yang la recortó para su exhibición hasta los 188 minutos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"A Brighter Summer Day","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"L'histoire dans les années soixante de Xiao Si'r, jeune adolescent, fils d'un réfugié politique chinois qui vit à Taïwan. Comme tous les jeunes gens de sa condition il fréquente les gangs qui se mènent une guerre sans merci."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Um Dia Quente de Verão","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Baseado em uma história verídica sobre um conflito entre duas gangues de jovens, a namorada de um garoto de 14 anos entra em conflito com o chefe de uma gangue por uma razão pouco clara, até que finalmente o conflito atinge um clímax violento."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"고령가 소년 살인 사건","runtime":237,"tagline":"소년, 소녀를 만나다","homepage":"","overview":"14살 소년 샤오쓰는 국어 성적이 나쁘다는 이유로 중학교 주간부에서 야간부로 반을 옮기게 되고 ‘소공원’파와 어울려 다닌다. 그러던 중 샤오쓰는 양호실에서 밍이라는 이름의 소녀를 만나게 된다. 소녀는 ‘소공원’파의 보스 허니의 여자로 허니는 샤오밍을 차지하기 위해 경쟁조직인 ‘217’파의 보스를 죽이고 은둔 중이다. 보스의 부재로 통제력을 상실한 ‘소공원’파는 보스 자리를 두고 혼란에 빠지고 돌연 허니가 돌아오게 되면서 ‘소공원’파 내부와 ‘217’파간의 대립이 격해진다. 그리고 밍을 사랑하게 된 샤오쓰도 이들의 싸움에 휘말리게 되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Parlak Bir Yaz Günü","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Xiao Si'r Tayvan'da yaşayan bir mültecinin genç oğludur. Ancak Tayvan'da bir mülteci olarak yaşamak hiç de kolay değildir. Gerçek bir olaydan alınan filmde Tayvan'da birbirine düşman iki çeteden birbirine aşık olan 14 yaşında iki gencin hikayesi ele alınıyor."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"牯嶺街少年殺人事件","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事背景是60年代的臺北，父子檔明星張國柱和張震分別飾演循規蹈矩的公務員，和正在念建國中學夜間部的初二學生小四。小四和他那一群十多歲的朋友組成小幫派，跟其他小太保的幫派時常搏殺。小四喜歡上老大HONEY 的女友小明，不料她並非自己所想的那樣可愛，遂在種種因素影響下於牯嶺街上誤殺了小明。  本片野心勃勃地透過一件真人真事來刻劃整個轉型期的臺灣社會面貌，自大陸撤退來臺灣的上一代在臺灣土生土長的下一代各有難念的經，本片只是一個深具時代氣息和人文關懷的小縮影。  彈子房、小公園、冰果室、貓王的音樂和收音機裡聯考放榜的唱名，《牯嶺街少年殺人事件》再現的不只是當年震驚社會的真實殺人事件，也重現了五零年代台灣白色恐怖時期的肅殺氣氛。眷村少年派系鬥毆、爭風吃醋；張震飾演的小四，太早耗磨的純真理想，太快早熟早逝的青春，一如暗夜裡明滅的燈火，只剩對那個時代的追憶與嘆息。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"牯嶺街少年殺人事件","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"大陸からの移住組の一家がこうむる圧力は、さらに露骨なものとなって少年シャオスーを巻き込んでいく。彼の恋した少女ミンは、彼らのボスの情婦という噂がある。そのボスは、敵グループのボスと一騎討ちの最中、車にはねられて死んでしまう。やがてスーはミンとの交際を注意され、怒って中学を退学する。だがミンは、スーの親友で軍人の息子マーと付き合いはじめていた……。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"牯嶺街少年殺人事件","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"小四因考試失準進入夜間班，和周圍終日廝混的幫派少年格格不入，直到他遇到清純憂鬱的女孩小明。二人壓抑中情愫萌生，卻注定悲劇收場。漆黑的夜裏，明滅的燈光，留聲機裏的搖滾樂……導演借一宗轟動全國的殺人事件，追懷 60 年代台灣社會：物質匱乏、白色恐怖、政治鬥爭。交織出一段昏暗苦澀的青春。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Gu Ling Jie Shao Nian Sha Ren Shi Jian","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na een tijd deel van Japan uitgemaakt te hebben, kwam Taiwan na de Tweede Wereldoorlog weer in Chinese handen. De Chinese overheid stimuleerde haar inwoners om naar het eiland te trekken, om daar een nieuw bestaan op te bouwen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"A Brighter Summer Day","runtime":237,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En maratonfilm som speglar Taiwans identitetskris i efterkrigstiden i några ungdomars öden och äventyr."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Яркий летний день","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Тайбэйские подростки 60-х годов живут в мире, где царит отчуждение и неуверенность в будущем. Повествование разворачивается вокруг отношений 14-летнего сына государственного служащего и подружки одного из главарей уличных банд."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"O zi mai însorită de vară","runtime":237,"tagline":"Un băiat experimentează prima iubire, prietenii și nedreptăți crescând în anii 1960 în Taiwan.","homepage":"","overview":"Taipei, 1960. Un student de 14 ani, Chang Chen, cunoscut de toată lumea sub numele de Xiao Si'r („Micul Patru”, deoarece este al patrulea din cinci copii), primise o notă proastă la o materie anul trecut. Deși la toate celelalte materii a avut succes și este de fapt un elev bun, a trebuit să treacă de la „școala de zi” la „școala serală”. Tatăl său, un funcționar guvernamental din clasa de mijloc, este nemulțumit pentru că școlile serale au o reputație proastă. La școala, care se caracterizează prin strictețe militară, profesorii se adresează adesea elevilor doar cu numerele atribuite. Preocupările tatălui nu sunt neîntemeiate: ciocniri brutale izbucnesc în mod repetat între Micii Băieți Din Park și Cei 217, două bande de tineri."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Chłopiec z ulicy Guling","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chłopiec doświadcza pierwszej miłości, przyjaźni i niesprawiedliwości, dorastając w Tajwanie w latach 60."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"A Brighter Summer Day","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A differenza degli altri film del regista, tutti ambientati nel contemporaneo, A Brighter Summer Day si svolge nei drammatici anni '60 dell'isola di Taiwan, segnati dalla politica del governo locale e dai difficili rapporti tra nativi e gli immigrati dalla Cina Popolare insieme al governo del Kuomintang e del suo leader Chiang Kai-shek, dopo la vittoria di Mao Tse-tung. Nelle sue quattro ore, A Brighter Summer Day mostra un episodio di cronaca che ebbe per protagonista un ragazzo, colpevole di aver ucciso una coetanea."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Jasný letní den","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Děj se odehrává v jediném dni školního roku v Taipei počátkem šedesátých let a zobrazuje zemi stále ještě se vzpamatovávající z rozvratného přílivu čínských nacionalistů v roce 1948. Taiwan se zmítá mezi komunismem a demokracií, nacionalismem a liberalismem, ve zmatcích, odcizení a nejistotě vedoucích občas k oslabující vykořeněnosti."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Một Ngày Hè Tươi Sáng Hơn","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Khi Si'r 14 tuổi yêu Ming, thủ lĩnh của một băng đảng trẻ trong địa phương, anh bắt đầu ngày càng tham gia vào băng nhóm, dần dần cuốn anh vào một thế giới bạo lực."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"یک روز تابستانی روشن‌تر","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"پسری در حال رشد در دهه ۱۹۶۰ تایوان اولین عشق، دوستی‌ها و بی‌عدالتی‌ها را تجربه می‌کند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《牯岭街少年杀人事件》是一部改编自台湾青少年真实杀人事件的电影作品。故事讲述了20世纪60年代初在台湾的一宗杀人事件的始末。结识小明 前，小四 是典型的乖仔，是父母的希望和兄妹的骄傲（一家人指望他考上名牌大学将来提升全家的社会地位），他有一个喜欢摇滚乐的自称“小猫王（王启赞）”的好友，两人虽会去树林看人幽会，但过的是与周围诸多在“小公园”混的少年人完全两样的生活。喜欢上小明后，小四便像跌进一个无底深渊，开始被外界的各种力量牵着鼻子走。新识仰慕对象honey 猝死，一向敬重的父亲的自尊与精神因为某次事件严重受损，加上将一次次“欺骗玩弄”他感情的小明“看透”，血气方刚又有很强道德感的小四终于走上犯罪的道路，期望用自己的刀结束事件的根源。但小四不知的是，他眼中的根源只是这条食物链中微不足道的一环。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Gu Ling Jie Shao Nian Sha Ren Shi Jian","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Na een tijd deel van Japan uitgemaakt te hebben, kwam Taiwan na de Tweede Wereldoorlog weer in Chinese handen. De Chinese overheid stimuleerde haar inwoners om naar het eiland te trekken, om daar een nieuw bestaan op te bouwen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"BE","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Ein Sommer zum Verlieben","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Taipei im Jahr 1960. Der 14-jährige Schüler Chang Chen, von allen Xiao Si'r („kleine Vier“, da er das vierte von fünf Kindern ist) genannt, hatte im letzten Jahr in einem Fach eine mangelhafte Note erhalten. Obwohl alle anderen Fächer erfolgreich liefen und er eigentlich ein guter Schüler ist, musste er von der „Tagesschule“ auf die „Abendschule“ wechseln. Sein Vater, ein Regierungsbeamter aus dem Mittelstand, ist darüber unglücklich, denn die abendlich stattfindenden Schulen besitzen einen schlechten Ruf. Auf der von militärischer Strenge geprägten Schule werden die Schüler von den Lehrern oft nur mit den ihnen zugeteilten Nummern angesprochen. Die Bedenken des Vaters sind nicht grundlos: Zwischen den Little Park Boys und den 217s, zwei Jugendbanden, kommt es immer wieder zu brutalen Auseinandersetzungen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"AT","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Ein Sommer zum Verlieben","runtime":236,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Taipei im Jahr 1960. Der 14-jährige Schüler Chang Chen, von allen Xiao Si'r („kleine Vier“, da er das vierte von fünf Kindern ist) genannt, hatte im letzten Jahr in einem Fach eine mangelhafte Note erhalten. Obwohl alle anderen Fächer erfolgreich liefen und er eigentlich ein guter Schüler ist, musste er von der „Tagesschule“ auf die „Abendschule“ wechseln. Sein Vater, ein Regierungsbeamter aus dem Mittelstand, ist darüber unglücklich, denn die abendlich stattfindenden Schulen besitzen einen schlechten Ruf. Auf der von militärischer Strenge geprägten Schule werden die Schüler von den Lehrern oft nur mit den ihnen zugeteilten Nummern angesprochen. Die Bedenken des Vaters sind nicht grundlos: Zwischen den Little Park Boys und den 217s, zwei Jugendbanden, kommt es immer wieder zu brutalen Auseinandersetzungen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"CH","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Яскравий літній день","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Історія розгортається на початку 60-х у Тайбеї. Після втечі на Тайвань мільйони китайців переживають непрості часи непевності у майбутньому. В цих умовах діти створюють вуличні банди. У центрі сюжету школяр Сяо Си та його стосунки з вчителями, рідними, друзями та дівчатами."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Um Belo Dia de Verão","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Baseado numa história verídica, principalmente num conflito entre dois bandos de jovens, a namorada de um rapaz de 14 anos entra em conflito com o chefe de um dos bandos por uma razão pouco clara, até que finalmente o conflito chega a um clímax violento."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เด็กชายคนหนึ่งได้สัมผัสกับรักครั้งแรก มิตรภาพ และความอยุติธรรมในช่วงที่เติบโตในไต้หวันในช่วงทศวรรษ 1960"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":25538,"adult":false,"title":"Yi Yi","video":false,"overview":"A Taipei family faces personal and moral uncertainty as everyday events test their relationships and sense of purpose.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8502,"vote_count":644,"poster_path":"/mR8dSQZI8X6Z1NClJhFrtJp636z.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-20","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/x903dx8Km6XNLFEmvbXc98vePSV.jpg","original_title":"一一","original_language":"zh"},{"id":75181,"adult":false,"title":"Crazy n' the City","video":false,"overview":"Tensions arise when Jack Chan, a spineless constable who regards his work as a job but not a career, is partnered with an energetic and conscientious policewoman, Man Liu. When a serial killer emerges in Hong Kong, Man Liu swears to catch him. Jack is impressed by her bravery and decides to secretly protect her.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9278,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/l3r7K14JVPL1rTYvJm5l2Yp2qhw.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-14","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/dCMFFUCNS05uahg7vFxrUoght7p.jpg","original_title":"神經俠侶","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1255854,"adult":false,"title":"Vavel the Band","video":false,"overview":"Vavel was a very successful band in the 1980s Greece. They were one of the first Greek heavy metal bands to release LP and became famous among the scene for the unique set design of their concerts. However, since the formation, their members dreamed of achieving an international career. That dream led them to a train station outside Dusseldorf.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0214,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/oVosTUOte9aDM2hlFSem8MSwbSr.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-08","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/uJLHFeYMLgkXFxwpWpj4O23M8iv.jpg","original_title":"Vavel the Band","original_language":"el"},{"id":1030404,"adult":false,"title":"有影嘸影","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0143,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1996-05-07","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"有影嘸影","original_language":"zh"},{"id":121878,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Supper","video":false,"overview":"The story of two warring generals fighting for control of China at the end of the Qin Dynasty.","genre_ids":[28,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6014,"vote_count":30,"poster_path":"/4wIc97ChG4CIc4rXExNmX2IqWuk.jpg","release_date":"2012-05-07","vote_average":6.15,"backdrop_path":"/qslDmlACPw3OUGIhJSYkF6Xc0VK.jpg","original_title":"王的盛宴","original_language":"zh"},{"id":270200,"adult":false,"title":"Young Rebels","video":false,"overview":"From Amir Shervan, the director of SAMURAI COP, comes another great 90's action classic. One man (Johnny Greene) teams up with another (Tadashi Yamashita) to take down the cartel run and its evil leader (Robert Z'Dar).","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2709,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/2YBmk4Hr6B7JmONde56CuLO8LzA.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-31","vote_average":3.7,"backdrop_path":"/lEZdQW8DoTDzImcRqOgsLeZAwMd.jpg","original_title":"Young Rebels","original_language":"en"},{"id":1528987,"adult":false,"title":"The death of the Conducător (a Christmas film)","video":false,"overview":"A visual collage following the rise and fall of infamous 20th century Romanian dictator Nicolae Ceaușescu","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1109,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/pe27QB2d8pIKB31f7tSuGjDCLOa.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-12","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The death of the Conducător (a Christmas film)","original_language":"en"},{"id":83517,"adult":false,"title":"Speed Angels","video":false,"overview":"After being recruited by a race car driver coach, a female taxi driver joins the Speed Angels racing team.","genre_ids":[28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.659,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/7nlvlXQnhY5uRpAocHPX2S0j1ZC.jpg","release_date":"2011-12-29","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/jUDBwNidjA6G8KXF53qsIZbqW7J.jpg","original_title":"極速天使","original_language":"zh"},{"id":106828,"adult":false,"title":"Evidence","video":false,"overview":"A haunting look at children watching television.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2875,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1995-10-02","vote_average":5.842,"backdrop_path":"/to1j8mucmB38TbKFjnC8PO3SFpy.jpg","original_title":"Evidence","original_language":"en"},{"id":1001377,"adult":false,"title":"Salem","video":false,"overview":"14-year-old Grasshoppers gang member Djibril leads a dangerous existence in a Marseille slum, along with his pregnant girlfriend Camilla who belongs to a rival gang, the Crickets. When Djibril is manipulated into killing the young Cricket Mahad, war breaks out. Djibril is haunted by the curse Mahad spat out as he lay dying, and begins to communicate with the spirit world. Convinced that global apocalypse is imminent, he embarks on a crazy plan to flee with Camilla and their unborn child – the only one capable of saving them all from Mahad’s malediction. But the law catches up with him. Now, after 12 years in prison and a secure psychiatric unit, Djibril will do whatever it takes to find his daughter and convince her to fulfil his prophecy.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3382,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/jb04DehPpnMnsra9N4PK7VZmyAg.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-29","vote_average":5.405,"backdrop_path":"/8H5PHiNfaHf0vjmp5mSWFKkLgGN.jpg","original_title":"Salem","original_language":"fr"},{"id":24774,"adult":false,"title":"The Idiot","video":false,"overview":"A gentle, war-shattered ex-soldier, Kinji Kameda, arrives in wintry Hokkaidō and is pulled into a volatile tangle of love and pity between the disgraced Taeko Nasu, the proud Ayako, and his possessive friend Akama. Kameda’s saintly compassion exposes everyone’s wounds, steering the quartet toward jealousy, violence, and inexorable tragedy. Adapted from Dostoevsky’s novel.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8876,"vote_count":123,"poster_path":"/4a6zhVb9a9KEnxNevKrJLfuGhm4.jpg","release_date":"1951-05-23","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/i1I90iYpzA49bZUMV89z22gXu4K.jpg","original_title":"白痴","original_language":"ja"},{"id":51520,"adult":false,"title":"Blind Mountain","video":false,"overview":"Young student Bai Xuemei is cheated and sold as a wife by human traffickers to a remote village. Raped and beaten, she leads the life of a sex slave and child-bearer with no hope of escape because of the villagers apathy and selfishness.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5165,"vote_count":74,"poster_path":"/gabbyvJQ8i48qgJYesABMR7S5bc.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-19","vote_average":7.662,"backdrop_path":"/phI5uHzKbNwiADYVJebqVqUeZWI.jpg","original_title":"盲山","original_language":"zh"},{"id":423248,"adult":false,"title":"Moon Young","video":false,"overview":"Mute Moon-young records people's faces with her small camcorder on the subway. One day, she avoids her drunk father at home and films Hee-soo who is crying over saying goodbye to her boyfriend and gets caught. The two feel some sort of kinship and become closer.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.567,"vote_count":19,"poster_path":"/6gvSLdOVW7Xy3zbZbrYDT6x180.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-12","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/n4uP0r6piqZdueiLWjZYbYsjHay.jpg","original_title":"문영","original_language":"ko"},{"id":64544,"adult":false,"title":"Boyfriends and Girlfriends","video":false,"overview":"Middle-class Parisian suburbs: Blanche and Léa, office worker and student, meet and become friends. Léa is going out with Fabien, but is thinking of leaving him. Blanche falls for Léa's handsome and witty friend Alexandre, but is tongue-tied whenever she meets him. Léa goes on holiday and Blanche, still smitten with the dashing Alexandre, begins to get to know Fabien.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3669,"vote_count":127,"poster_path":"/obfJYuVMGFZRlMeNQklFlvhShFu.jpg","release_date":"1987-08-26","vote_average":7.11,"backdrop_path":"/7P7Gd5iiqISDI3UUsmryBUK8rMj.jpg","original_title":"L'Ami de mon amie","original_language":"fr"},{"id":46799,"adult":false,"title":"The Third Part of the Night","video":false,"overview":"Set during the Nazi occupation of Poland, the story follows Michał, who witnesses the murder of his mother, wife and child and then is hurled into a life that literally is not his own; a surreal world littered with trapdoors, doppelgängers and wormholes.","genre_ids":[10752,18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6037,"vote_count":92,"poster_path":"/26bTBcH1SVn92dVNr6X9JQxXlxe.jpg","release_date":"1972-01-04","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/y9NXfEz8p1IiR8Ug4vpa3MiI8lJ.jpg","original_title":"Trzecia część nocy","original_language":"pl"},{"id":786584,"adult":false,"title":"Dawn of the Beast","video":false,"overview":"Aiming to find the Bigfoot, a group of graduate students venture deep into an area of the Northeastern wilderness known for its strange creature sightings. Soon, they learn that there is a much more sinister evil lurking in the woods, the Wendigo, and once the spirit knows you’re there, they will come for you. Who will survive in a battle between the two most notorious monsters of the forest?","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2945,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/hZGx57ShJ3IUeZNxEbOMinW4wea.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-06","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/bt4l2wWtG3lzZvNcOcDgnul1NQd.jpg","original_title":"Dawn of the Beast","original_language":"en"},{"id":449927,"adult":false,"title":"Chasing the Dragon","video":false,"overview":"An illegal immigrant from Mainland China sneaks into the corrupt British-colonized Hong Kong in 1963, transforming himself into a ruthless drug lord.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9235,"vote_count":131,"poster_path":"/Lc0XGNZmsFe3uA1UMqhlBiJSY4.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-28","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/6WFWXiwe9rpaXsiuTtM351B2Il9.jpg","original_title":"追龍","original_language":"cn"},{"id":53423,"adult":false,"title":"Shoulder Arms","video":false,"overview":"An American doughboy, stationed in France during the Great War, goes on a daring mission behind enemy lines and becomes a hero.","genre_ids":[35,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4444,"vote_count":191,"poster_path":"/lxn5foteeZbDGIEfSahW4UMxnTC.jpg","release_date":"1918-10-20","vote_average":6.827,"backdrop_path":"/b87wEkeuVDDjZOYM4IdUgILnKtZ.jpg","original_title":"Shoulder Arms","original_language":"en"},{"id":78450,"adult":false,"title":"Terrorizers","video":false,"overview":"An uncompromising look into urban life from the eyes of a voyeuristic photographer, a rebellious teenager, and a married couple teetering on the edge of adultery.","genre_ids":[18,80,9648,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0522,"vote_count":166,"poster_path":"/7uX1PVn9Tob81hqwdzAjqPeaXZO.jpg","release_date":"1986-12-19","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/vooAbSV1zJqwRNHxCxFQ8fVDm38.jpg","original_title":"恐怖份子","original_language":"zh"},{"id":161285,"adult":false,"title":"In the Heat of the Sun","video":false,"overview":"Beijing, 1970s. The Cultural Revolution has driven most adults to the provinces leaving 14-year-old Monkey and his pals have free reign over the city. They hang around, get up to no good, and discover that unsolvable mystery known as \"girls.\"","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9157,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/ky7JiHPlwb0vKNSwWgXHQnQs6d7.jpg","release_date":"1995-08-21","vote_average":7.813,"backdrop_path":"/9YhcK0LSe9xWvIV6zgNZGDA7ZIb.jpg","original_title":"阳光灿烂的日子","original_language":"zh"}],"similar_content":[{"id":167,"adult":false,"title":"K-PAX","video":false,"overview":"Prot is a patient at a mental hospital who claims to be from a far away planet. His psychiatrist tries to help him, only to begin to doubt his own explanations.","genre_ids":[878,18,9648],"popularity":3.1759,"vote_count":2664,"poster_path":"/tafXZX0I6rso7EyoEzfygfTqxq6.jpg","release_date":"2001-10-26","vote_average":7.204,"backdrop_path":"/m9ELo5SDNZvp7CGbSVIMYBeY8wl.jpg","original_title":"K-PAX","original_language":"en"},{"id":179,"adult":false,"title":"The Interpreter","video":false,"overview":"After Silvia Broome, an interpreter at United Nations headquarters, overhears plans of an assassination, an American Secret Service agent is sent to investigate.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":2.4155,"vote_count":1531,"poster_path":"/wTidq3J9fh8sEOAlD8WZFHVLSuB.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-08","vote_average":6.309,"backdrop_path":"/A5mBIAtZOqVpAVUXolwtOnaQcZc.jpg","original_title":"The Interpreter","original_language":"en"},{"id":182,"adult":false,"title":"The Good German","video":false,"overview":"An American journalist arrives in Berlin just after the end of World War Two. He becomes involved in a murder mystery surrounding a dead GI who washes up at a lakeside mansion during the Potsdam negotiations between the Allied powers. Soon his investigation connects with his search for his married pre-war German lover.","genre_ids":[18,9648,10749,53,10752],"popularity":0.9333,"vote_count":339,"poster_path":"/3LjHC2CWDkzoiPehf3GViujws0.jpg","release_date":"2006-12-15","vote_average":5.805,"backdrop_path":"/vr9xAWJeIkYJWAYmIov5WNHEAf6.jpg","original_title":"The Good German","original_language":"en"},{"id":185,"adult":false,"title":"A Clockwork Orange","video":false,"overview":"In a near-future Britain, young Alexander DeLarge and his pals get their kicks beating and raping anyone they please. When not destroying the lives of others, Alex swoons to the music of Beethoven. The state, eager to crack down on juvenile crime, gives an incarcerated Alex the option to undergo an invasive procedure that'll rob him of all personal agency. In a time when conscience is a commodity, can Alex change his tune?","genre_ids":[878,80],"popularity":9.2739,"vote_count":13611,"poster_path":"/4sHeTAp65WrSSuc05nRBKddhBxO.jpg","release_date":"1971-10-28","vote_average":8.18,"backdrop_path":"/nLFxvLokHe3bQmrmAfljIfax2jQ.jpg","original_title":"A Clockwork Orange","origin